org.mozilla.gecko.util

Class GeckoBundle

  • Object
    • org.mozilla.gecko.util.GeckoBundle
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable

    public final class GeckoBundle
extends Object
implements android.os.Parcelable
    A lighter-weight version of Bundle that adds support for type coercion (e.g. int to double) in order to better cooperate with JS objects.
